    <h1>My Favorite Recipes</h1>
    <p>Elegant Chocolate-Dipped Treats</p>
    <h3>List of Ingredients</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>24 large strawberries</li>
        <li>1 cup semisweet chocolate pieces</li>
        <li>1 teaspoon vegetable oil</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h3>Directions</h3>
    <ol>
        <li>Line 2 baking sheets with waxed paper.</li>
        <li>Rinse and dry the strawberries.</li>
        <li>Melt chocolate in microwave or on top of double boiler over simmering water.</li>
        <li>Stir in vegetable oil.</li>
        <li>Dip berry to coat, then place on waxed paper; let stand to harden.</li>
        <li>To speed firming, refrigerate 6 minutes.</li>
    </ol>
    
    <p>For gourmet-shop flair, before chocolate sets, dip in shredded coconut or chopped nuts.</p>

